### ---------------------------------------
### ⭐ REVIEWS
### ---------------------------------------

### Get reviews for item
GET {{api}}/reviews/1

### Create review
POST {{api}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Muy buen trato",
  "fk_items_id": 1,
  "fk_reviewed_id": 2
}

### Delete review
DELETE {{api}}/reviews/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

